'''小湯瑪斯·藍道爾·曼恩'''（{{lang-en|Thomas Randall Mann, Jr.}}，{{bd|1991年|9月27日}}），美國男演員。他因出演電影《[[派對X計劃|派對X計劃]]》（2012）、《[[女巫獵人|女巫獵人]]》（2013）、《[[我們的故事未完待續|我們的故事未完待續]]》（2015）和《[[金剛：骷髏島|金剛：骷髏島]]》（2017）而聞名<ref>{{cite web |author=Jeff Sneider Variety March 23, 2012 |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/sns-201203231732reedbusivarietynvr1118051831mar23,0,5661194.story |title='Project X' actor to star in 'King Dork': Thomas Mann tapped for comedy from Will Ferrell and Adam McKay banner |publisher=chicagotribune.com |date=2012-03-23 |accessdate=2012-08-06 |archive-date=2012-07-30 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120730015754/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/sns-201203231732reedbusivarietynvr1118051831mar23,0,5661194.story |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

==私人生活==
湯瑪斯·曼恩生於[[波特蘭_(俄勒岡州)|波特蘭]]，成長於[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]][[達拉斯|達拉斯]]<ref name=nextmovie>{{cite web |url=http://www.nextmovie.com/blog/thomas-mann-interview-project-x/ |title=Next Factor Q&A: Thomas Mann Fights for His Right to Party in ‘Project X’ |publisher=NextMovie.com |date=2012-02-27 |accessdate=2012-08-06 |quote=...the now 20-year-old Thomas Mann, who grew up in Dallas, Texas... |archive-date=2012-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120501083255/http://www.nextmovie.com/blog/thomas-mann-interview-project-x |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的父親是一位建築工程主管<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/thomas-mann-sundance-2015/|title=Mann About Sundance|work=Interview Magazine|accessdate=2017-02-26|archive-date=2017-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170530132326/http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/thomas-mann-sundance-2015|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曼恩在17歲搬去加利福尼亞州尋求演出機會前曾短暫就讀{{le|東普萊諾高中|Plano East Senior High School}}<ref>{{cite web|title=About Thomas|url=http://thomas-mann.us/about-thomas/|website=Thomas Mann Online|accessdate=2016-12-30|date=2016-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161231074521/http://thomas-mann.us/about-thomas/|archive-date=2016-12-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==演藝生涯==
===早期工作===
2009年，曼恩於[[尼可國際兒童頻道|尼可國際兒童頻道]]情景喜劇電視系列《[[愛卡莉|愛卡莉]]》首次亮相表演，他在裡面飾演傑夫瑞（Jeffrey）。於同年參與《愛卡莉》演出後，曼恩在《[[左右不逢源|左右不逢源]]》裡飾演布蘭登·尼可拉斯（Brendan Nichols）<ref name=nextmovie1>{{cite news|last=Harris|first=Scott|title=Watch Out for Thomas Mann, Who Just Might Be The Man|url=http://www.nextmovie.com/blog/thomas-mann-is-the-man/|accessdate=2012-12-10|newspaper=NextMovie|date=2011-04-22|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231124/http://www.nextmovie.com/blog/thomas-mann-is-the-man/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2010年，曼恩於喜劇電影《[[派對X計劃|派對X計劃]]》飾演主角<ref>{{cite web |last=Fleming |first=Mike |url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/04/todd-phillips-joel-silver-plan-to-tap-unknowns-for-mystery-laffer-project-x/ |title=Todd Phillips, Joel Silver Plan To Tap Unknowns For Mystery Laugher 'Project X' |publisher=Deadline.com |date= |accessdate=2012-08-06 |archive-date=2014-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140803233758/http://www.deadline.com/2010/04/todd-phillips-joel-silver-plan-to-tap-unknowns-for-mystery-laffer-project-x/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 他原本被告知無法試鏡，因為製作人只希望找沒有演戲經驗的人；曼恩試鏡七次後最終獲選<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.buzzinebollywood.com/interviews/international-film-interview-thomas-mann-oliver-cooper-jonathan-daniel-brown-project-x-02282012 |title=Film Interview: Cast Of 'Project X' | Buzzine.Com |publisher=Buzzinebollywood.com |date=2012-03-02 |accessdate=2012-08-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130708095217/http://buzzinebollywood.com/interviews/international-film-interview-thomas-mann-oliver-cooper-jonathan-daniel-brown-project-x-02282012 |archivedate=2013-07-08 }}</ref>。電影注重於曼恩飾演的角色——湯瑪斯身上，他在家裡舉辦生日派對，結果變成難以收拾的巨大場面。該片於同年6月在[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]開拍，預算為一千兩百萬元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://collider.com/exclusive-todd-phillips-talks-project-x/22609/ |title=Exclusive: Todd Phillips Talks 'Project  X' |publisher=Collider.com |date= |accessdate=2012-08-06 |archive-date=2012-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120302160945/http://collider.com/exclusive-todd-phillips-talks-project-x/22609 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影續集計畫也於2012年有了進展<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/project-x-sequel-warner-bros-michael-bacall-297235 | title = 'Project X' Sequel in the Works at Warner Bros. (Exclusive) | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | first = Borys | last = Kit | date = 2012-03-06 | accessdate = 2012-08-06 | archive-date = 2012-12-25 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6DAEjgYK9?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/project-x-sequel-warner-bros-michael-bacall-297235 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2012年3月，曼恩進入小說改編電影《{{le|呆子王|King Dork}}》演出的最後洽談階段<ref name=variety032312>{{cite news|last=Sneider|first=Jeff|title='Project X' actor to star in 'King Dork'|url=http://variety.com/2012/film/news/project-x-actor-to-star-in-king-dork-1118051831/|accessdate=2012-12-10|newspaper=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2012-03-23|archive-date=2013-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031015919/http://variety.com/2012/film/news/project-x-actor-to-star-in-king-dork-1118051831/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影由{{le|格雷·桑切斯製片公司|Gary Sanchez Productions}}於2006年11月買下電影版權，格雷·桑切斯製片公司由[[威爾·法洛|威爾·法洛]]和[[亞當·麥凱|亞當·麥凱]]創立<ref name=punknews>{{cite news|title=King Dork movie adaptation status update, release date for follow up|url=http://www.punknews.org/article/33490/king-dork-movie-adaptation-status-update-release-date-for-follow-up|accessdate=2012-12-10|date=2009-05-11|archive-date=2012-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020231503/http://www.punknews.org/article/33490/king-dork-movie-adaptation-status-update-release-date-for-follow-up|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，曼恩與[[維多利亞·嘉絲蒂|維多利亞·嘉絲蒂]]一起演出電影《{{le|瘋狂萬聖夜|Fun Size}}》，他在裡面飾演羅斯福（Roosevelt），該電影於[[美國|美國]]時間2012年10月26日上映。電影淪為[[票房毒藥|票房毒藥]]並且受到評論家批評<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.teen.com/2012/10/23/celebrities/the-new-star/thomas-mann-facts-trivia-bio-pictures/|title=Thomas Mann Bio, Photos, Facts: Fun Size Actor Trivia - Teen.com|work=Teen.com|access-date=2017-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924114037/http://www.teen.com/2012/10/23/celebrities/the-new-star/thomas-mann-facts-trivia-bio-pictures/|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://scottalanmendelson.blogspot.com/2012/11/why-box-office-failure-of-fun-size-is.html|title=Mendelson's Memos|author=Scott Mendelson|publisher=|accessdate=2017-02-26|archive-date=2017-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171211104915/http://scottalanmendelson.blogspot.com/2012/11/why-box-office-failure-of-fun-size-is.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年，曼恩演出《[[女巫獵人|女巫獵人]]》飾演班（Ben）。電影於美國時間2013年1月25日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hansel_and_gretel_witch_hunters/trailers/11175051|title=Hansel & Gretel: Witch Hunters: Thomas Mann On His Character|work=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2017-02-26|archive-date=2016-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020142049/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hansel_and_gretel_witch_hunters/trailers/11175051/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，曼恩演出小說改編同名電影《[[美麗魔物|美麗魔物]]》，曼恩在裡面飾演林克（Link），電影其他演員包括[[薇拉·戴維絲|薇拉·戴維絲]]和[[艾瑪·湯普遜|艾瑪·湯普遜]]。該片於2013年2月14日上映而且總共賺得六千萬全球票房，不過預算也是六千萬元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cinesnob.net/thomas-mann-zoey-deutch-beautiful-creatures/|title=Thomas Mann & Zoey Deutch – Beautiful Creatures|publisher=|accessdate=2017-02-26|archive-date=2017-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171211160945/http://www.cinesnob.net/thomas-mann-zoey-deutch-beautiful-creatures/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曼恩之後與[[莎拉·伯格|莎拉·伯格]]和[[詹姆斯·馬斯登|詹姆斯·馬斯登]]演出《{{le|酷我隨行 (電影)|As Cool as I Am (film)|酷我隨行}}》。該電影由{{le|IFC電影|IFC Films}}發行於2013年6月21日<ref>{{cite av media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZTFjTyMCC90|title=As Cool As I Am Official Trailer 2013 (HD) - Claire Danes, James Marsden, Thomas Mann|date=2013-05-21|publisher=|via=YouTube|access-date=2017-02-26|archive-date=2017-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729024313/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZTFjTyMCC90|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===突破：2014年－至今===
2014年，曼恩演出《{{le|歡迎來到我的世界|Welcome to Me}}》飾演美術學生芮恩（Rainer Ybarra），電影演出演員包括[[克莉絲汀·薇格|克莉絲汀·薇格]]。電影於2014年9月5日在[[多倫多國際影展|多倫多國際影展]]全球首映，之後於2015年5月1日[[有限上映|有限上映]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tiff.net/festivals/thefestival/programmes/specialpresentations/welcome-to-me-1 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150718061120/http://www.tiff.net/festivals/thefestival/programmes/specialpresentations/welcome-to-me-1 |title=Special Presentations USA Shira Piven 88 minutes Welcome to Me |archivedate=2015-07-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/OurAlchemy/posts/908026595907746|title=Alchemy - TODAY IS THE BIG DAY! Welcome To Me is in... - Facebook|publisher=}}</ref>。2015年曼恩演出改編自{{le|傑西·安德魯斯|Jesse Andrews}}小說的電影《[[我們的故事未完待續|我們的故事未完待續]]》，電影於2015年1月25日在{{le|2015年日舞影展|2015 Sundance Film Festival}}首映。該片使[[福斯探照燈影業|福斯探照燈影業]]以一千兩百萬元獲得版權，創下有史以來福斯用最多錢買下影展電影版權的紀錄，電影於2015年6月12日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sundance-fox-searchlight-nears-record-766983|title=Sundance: Fox Searchlight Nears Record Deal for 'Me and Earl and the Dying Girl' (Exclusive)|author=Borys Kit|date=2015-01-25|work=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2017-02-26|archive-date=2017-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223085112/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sundance-fox-searchlight-nears-record-766983|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，曼恩演出《{{le|史丹佛監獄實驗 (電影)|The Stanford Prison Experiment (film)|史丹佛監獄實驗}}》，該片也有在2015年日舞影展上映，曼恩在裡面飾演囚犯416號。電影在2015年7月17日有限上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ifcfilms.com/films/the-stanford-prison-experiment|title=The Stanford Prison Experiment|work=IFC Films|accessdate=2017-02-26|archive-date=2017-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170309190414/http://www.ifcfilms.com/films/the-stanford-prison-experiment|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曼恩還有演出《[[刺客學妹|刺客學妹]]》，該片由[[蘇菲·特納|蘇菲·特納]]和[[海莉·史坦菲德|海莉·史坦菲德]]主演並於2015年5月29日在限定區域和[[隨選視訊|隨選視訊]]上映<ref name="bustle.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.bustle.com/articles/89046-the-lead-guy-in-me-and-earl-aka-thomas-mann-is-about-to-be-mega-famous-so|title=The Lead Guy In ‘Me And Earl’ AKA Thomas Mann Is About To Be Mega-Famous So Here's What To Know|first=Rachel|last=Simon|publisher=|accessdate=2016-12-14|archive-date=2017-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802210655/https://www.bustle.com/articles/89046-the-lead-guy-in-me-and-earl-aka-thomas-mann-is-about-to-be-mega-famous-so|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曼恩之後的電影角色包括《{{le|玩酷壞痞子|The Preppie Connection}}》飾演托比（Tobias Hammell）。電影描述一位私立學校學生利用網路在學校販售毒品<ref>{{cite web|url=http://coalitionfilms.com/the-preppie-connection/|title=THE PREPPIE CONNECTION|work=Coalition Films|accessdate=2017-02-26|archive-date=2014-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141115045651/http://coalitionfilms.com/the-preppie-connection|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在《怪怪惹人愛》（Some Freaks）裡曼恩飾演麥特（Matt）。他還有參與《艾蜜莉和提姆》（Emily & Tim）和《[[吾父吾血|吾父吾血]]》演出，其中後者與[[威廉·霍爾·梅西|威廉·霍爾·梅西]]和[[梅爾·吉勃遜|梅爾·吉勃遜]]合演<ref name="bustle.com"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/thomas-mann-zosia-mamet-join-outliving-emily-exclusive-1200974758/|title=Thomas Mann, Zosia Mamet Join ‘Outliving Emily’ (EXCLUSIVE)|author=Dave McNary|work=Variety|accessdate=2017-02-26|archive-date=2017-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206152307/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/thomas-mann-zosia-mamet-join-outliving-emily-exclusive-1200974758/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年，曼恩將與[[貝拉·索恩|貝拉·索恩]]一起演出《[[陰宅2|陰宅2]]》，該電影上映日未定<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/06/amityville-the-awakening-moves-off-summer-schedule-1202109296/|title=‘Amityville: The Awakening’ Moves Off Summer Schedule|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2017-06-07|publisher=deadline.com|accessdate=2017-08-06|archive-date=2017-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806140354/http://deadline.com/2017/06/amityville-the-awakening-moves-off-summer-schedule-1202109296/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後曼恩簽約與[[克蘿伊·摩蕾茲|克蘿伊·摩蕾茲]]和[[珍妮·斯蕾特|珍妮·斯蕾特]]共同演出電影《{{le|我發瘋的那段日子 (電影)|Brain on Fire (film)|我發瘋的那段日子}}》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/05/thomas-mann-jenny-slate-brain-on-fire-dakota-fanning-susannah-cahalan-1201432909/|title=Thomas Mann & Jenny Slate Join Dakota Fanning Film ‘Brain On Fire’ - Deadline|author=Mike Fleming Jr|work=Deadline|accessdate=2017-02-26|archive-date=2017-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170128085823/http://deadline.com/2015/05/thomas-mann-jenny-slate-brain-on-fire-dakota-fanning-susannah-cahalan-1201432909/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

